narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A class where you read key texts of theory and talk about how it can relate to art. Don't worry if you don't have familiarity with theory-this is the perfect introductory course. It will give you ideas to think about in your art making practice. Joy is also a wonderful teacher, so if she is teaching it, take it!
Summary: Read sources (Marx, Freud, de beauvoir). Discuss. Submit examples. Discuss. Write two papers.
I would especially recommend the class to practicing artists because the class and the material give you room to grow in your practice.
